    <item>
      <title>中国的“强势货币”梦遭遇特朗普回归</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/china-s-dream-of-powerful-currency-runs-into-trump-s-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平希望中国拥有足够稳定的“强势货币”，以在全球贸易中发挥越来越重要的作用。唐纳德·特朗普的回归似乎将挑战这一雄心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/china-s-dream-of-powerful-currency-runs-into-trump-s-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Nov 2024 00:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队在警方调查报告中支持赫格塞斯出任五角大楼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/trump-team-backs-pete-hegseth-for-pentagon-after-media-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在媒体报道警方正在调查针对皮特·赫格塞斯的性侵犯指控并且他的纹身引起一名陆军战友的担忧之后，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的团队支持他提名的国防部长人选皮特·赫格塞斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/trump-team-backs-pete-hegseth-for-pentagon-after-media-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 23:57:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命卡罗琳·莱维特为白宫新闻秘书</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/trump-names-karoline-leavitt-as-white-house-press-secretary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普任命卡罗琳·莱维特担任白宫新闻秘书，为其竞选团队的一位高级女发言人提供白宫最引人注目的职位之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/trump-names-karoline-leavitt-as-white-house-press-secretary</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 23:37:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗伯特·肯尼迪加剧了从医疗保险到堕胎等政策的不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/rfk-jr-fuels-uncertainty-on-policies-from-medicare-to-abortion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪被选为当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的首席卫生官员，这引发了政策观察家们的质疑：这位人选将如何处理属于他职权范围的一系列关键卫生政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/rfk-jr-fuels-uncertainty-on-policies-from-medicare-to-abortion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 23:26:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前中国人民银行官员称，若特朗普提高关税，中国将予以反击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/china-to-retaliate-if-trump-boosts-tariff-says-ex-pboc-official</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行前高级官员朱民表示，如果当选总统唐纳德·特朗普兑现对中国进口产品征收 60% 关税的承诺，中国将予以反击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/china-to-retaliate-if-trump-boosts-tariff-says-ex-pboc-official</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 22:31:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多告诉亚太经合组织，与特朗普合作绝非易事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/nothing-will-be-easy-in-working-with-trump-trudeau-tells-apec</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多在秘鲁利马亚太经济合作组织峰会上表示，与下一届唐纳德·特朗普政府合作对加拿大来说将是一个持续的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/nothing-will-be-easy-in-working-with-trump-trudeau-tells-apec</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 22:17:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普争取休会任命为何如此史无前例</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/recess-appointments-trump-s-bid-to-avoid-senate-confirmation-of-nominees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[学生们迫不及待地想要休息。美国参议院却竭尽全力避免这种情况发生。]]></description>
